\c 14
\s Dhavhidhi anoita sungano naHirami
\p
\v 1 Zvino Hiramu mambo weTire akatuma nhume kuna Dhavhidhi, nematanda emisidhari, nevavezi vemabwe nevavezi vematanda kumuvakira imba.
\v 2 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakaziva kuti Jehovha wakamusimbisa kuva mambo pamusoro paIsraeri, nokuti ushe hwake hwakasimidzirwa pamusoro nekuda kwevanhu vake Israeri.
\p
\v 3 Dhavhidhi ndokutora vamwe vakadzi paJerusarema, Dhavhidhi ndokubereka vamwe vanakomana nevanasikana.
\v 4 Zvino awa mazita evaaiva navo paJerusarema: Shamua, naShobhabhi, Natani, naSoromoni;
\v 5 naIbhari, naErishuwa, naEripareti;
\v 6 naNoga, naNefegi, naJafiya;
\v 7 naErishama, naBheeriyadha, naErifareti.
\p
\v 8 Zvino VaFirisitia vanzwa kuti Dhavhidhi azodzwa kuva mambo pamusoro paIsraeri wese, VaFirisitia vese ndokukwira kunotsvaka Dhavhidhi; Dhavhidhi ndoku\add zvi\add*nzwa, ndokubuda kuvarwisa.
\v 9 Zvino VaFirisitia vakasvika ndokuzviparadzira mumupata weRefaimu.
\v 10 Dhavhidhi ndokubvunza Jehovha, achiti: Ndokwira kurwisa VaFirisitia here? Muchavaisa muruoko rangu here? Jehovha ndokuti kwaari: Kwira, nokuti ndichavaisa muruoko rwako.
\v 11 Zvino vakakwira kuBhaari-Perazimi, Dhavhidhi ndokuvarovapo; Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Mwari wapazira muvavengi vangu neruoko rwangu, sekupazira kwemvura. Naizvozvo vakatumidza nzvimbo iyo Bhaari-Perazimi.
\v 12 Zvino vakasiya vamwari vavopo, Dhavhidhi ndokutaura \add kuti\add* vapiswe nemoto.
\v 13 VaFirisitia ndokupararirazve mumupata uyo.
\v 14 Ipapo Dhavhidhi akabvunza Mwari zve; Mwari akati kwaari: Usanovatevera; tsauka ubve kwavari, ugovavamba pakatarisana nemiti yemibharisami.
\v 15 Zvino kana uchinzwa kutinhira kokufamba pamisoro yemiti yemibharisami, ipapo unofanira kundorwa; nokuti Mwari akutungamirira kundoparadza hondo yaVaFirisitia.
\v 16 Dhavhidhi akaita sezvakarairwa naMwari; vakaparadza hondo yaVaFirisitia kubva paGibhiyoni kusvikira paGezeri.
\v 17 Mbiri yaDhavhidhi ikabudira kunyika dzese; Jehovha akavhundusa marudzi ese pamusoro pake.
